# Installation of GHC 7.8.4

## Installation Script

~~~
# get distribution  
cd $HOME/Downloads  

wget https://www.haskell.org/ghc/dist/7.8.4/ghc-7.8.4-x86_64-unknown-linux-deb7.tar.bz2   
tar xvfj ghc-7.8.4-x86_64-unknown-linux-deb7.tar.bz2  

cd ghc-7.8.4  

# install to  
mkdir $HOME/GHC-compiler/bin/ghc-7.8.4  

./configure --prefix=$HOME/GHC-compiler/bin/ghc-7.8.4  
make install

# cleanup: remove temporary files  
cd $HOME/Downloads  
rm -rfv ghc-7.8.4*
~~~

## Activation Script

~~~
cd $HOME/GHC-compiler/bin
rm -f ghc
ln -s `pwd`/ghc-7.8.4 ghc  
~~~